            . I am a watchman of Coleman-street. I went on duty at seven o'clock on the 23d of November, and at the end of <placeName id="t18261207-255-crimeloc1484">Finsbury-circus</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18261207-255-crimeloc1484" type="placeName" value="Finsbury-circus"></interp>
