                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-255-off1482 t18261207-255-crimeloc1484"></join> and London-wall, I saw the prisoner coming over some boards - I laid hold of him by his wooden-leg, and said, "You must go to the watch-house" - I searched him, and found this pipe and cock on him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18261207-255-person1407">
                  WILLIAM 
                  PAGE
               <interp inst="t18261207-255-person1407" type="surname" value="PAGE"></interp>
